# 16-scalability-performance-rules.mdc

---
description: Scalability requirements
---

Design for:

- Horizontal scaling
- Stateless services
- Efficient queries
- Caching readiness
- Background processing
- Async workflows

Performance considerations:

- Reduce unnecessary requests.
- Optimize payload sizes.
- Support pagination.
- Lazy load expensive resources.
